snippet.title: WWI: The First DogFighters - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Game developed in collaboration with Fernando Nigro, Jaelcio Dutra and Marcelo Chaves. All are students of Digital Games, at the Pontifícia Universidade Católica de Minas Gerais, located in Brazil.

Download now: https://marcelochaves.itch.io/ww1-the-first-dogfighters

Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/TheFirstDogFighters
